caption:
From the moment we got our little Goose on the loose, my life has been changed. He’s the sweetest little guy and always finds a way to make me feel loved ❤️  This #MentalHealthAwarenessMonth I want to thank Goose for being a light in my life and being there for me in every moment.
  
Together with @NuloPetFood, Goose and I invite you to take a moment today to thank your pet for all the comfort and support they give you by posting an incredible moment you’ve shared with them! Use the hashtag #TheyFuelUs and tag @NuloPetFood for a chance to be featured on Nulo’s social media. And remember to give your pet an extra cuddle or special treat today🦴🐶🐾
